{"tid":1479501,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"喂！今日光復紅土呀！！","createTime":"2019-08-17T02:43:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T05:30:03.000Z","uid":61672,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"61eeefd1357abb6aaec73987e4c1b59f59a30e57","tid":1479501,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T02:43:56.000Z","msg":"多國出聲援香港<br />\n而美國都準備利用香港做中美談判既籌碼<br />\n<br />\n呢一排大家切記be water <br />\n毋忘流水抗爭<br />\nhit and run <br />\n我地要有耐性，俾外國有時間插手幫助<br />\n香港人繼續放大其受害人身份，好讓外國有借口介入<br />\n<br />\n呢排好多鬼既傳聞<br />\n鬼一直都有<br />\n點捉都捉唔曬<br />\n唔好俾情緒/仇恨指導<br />\n<br />\n香港真正真民主路程準備開始<br />\n我地要有國際視野，世界觀感<br />\n為香港邁向民主，為下一代著想<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#612 721 811 <br />\n#五大訴求<br />\n#真雙普選 <br />\n<br />\n天佑香港<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a2afc3558ae856a4d6b8fbb6b318b6530429f5f","tid":1479501,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T02:44:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"224588ca087dd906161f1eeddf4bc94126c4eaa0","tid":1479501,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T02:44:27.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"60a2c18426cd76a4e59aa3d6a87f1c324d17e5b5","tid":1479501,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T02:44:37.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"6fd2d0810574d5279a98fc1633cc3309da93df51","tid":1479501,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T02:44:49.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"88473201f1298c28fc2f12c61766e95d9412d1bc","tid":1479501,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T02:44:59.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"4a3b81092de7f7672062b054b06308d915e64ac5","tid":1479501,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"